Name: summon
Title: Summon Command
DM: 1
The DM summon command is used to summon a player next to yourself.

<t t="Syntax:">/summon [player name]
<p><t t="See Also:">
^teleport^
^goto^
==========
Name: teleport
Title: Teleport Command
DM: 1
The DM teleport command is used to teleport yourself next to a player.

<t t="Syntax:">/teleport [player name]
<p><t t="See Also:">
^summon^
^goto^
==========
Name: goto
Title: Go To Command
DM: 1
The DM Go To command is used to teleport yourself to a specified map path, with optional X/Y coordinates on the map.

<t t="Syntax:">/goto [map path] [x] [y]
<p><t t="See Also:">
^teleport^
^summon^
==========
